</div><br />


<!-- Node: "Front Line Force moving skies." -->
<div class="body_box_header">Front Line Force moving skies.</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2203" title="View user profile.">pepper</a> on Thursday, September 9, 2004 - 11:58</small><br /><br />
Check out the <i>Front Line Force</i> Half-Life MOD, which has released a 8Mb movie of their work, illustrating the <i>moving skies</i> they created. The skies literally appear to be moving! According to the creators a mapper should have full control over the sky.<br><br>

