<!-- Node: "DOOM 3 Beta Patch is out!!" -->
<div class="body_box_header">DOOM 3 Beta Patch is out!!</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">Method</a> on Wednesday, September 8, 2004 - 00:01</small><br /><br />
Robert Duffy updated his <a href = "http://www.webdog.org/plans/313/">.plan</a> today talking about the new DOOM 3 beta patch. He said that the final patch, SDK and D3 Demo will be available shortly. He also said that the patch is only available from File Shack at www.shacknews.com and it fixes MP and game stability bugs. Get the patch <a href = "http://www.fileshack.com/file.x?fid=5392">here</a>.
