<!-- Node: "Vampire Slayer Half-Life mod final release" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Vampire Slayer Half-Life mod final release</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2203" title="View user profile.">pepper</a> on Tuesday, September 7, 2004 - 09:33</small><br /><br />
The final release of the Vampire Slayer modification for <br>Half-Life: Chapter 6.<br>
Here is what they say:<br><br>
  
<i>We are pleased to announce the release of 
Vampire  Slayer : Chapter VI. <br>
This is likely to be the final version of Vampire Slayer so I would like to take this opportunity to thank those who have helped over the last four years make the game what it was.</i><br><br>

Visit their site for more information:<br>
<a href="http://www.vsmod.com/"><b>Vampire Slayer</b></a>
