<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">Method</a> on Saturday, August 28, 2004 - 16:08</small><br /><br />
<a href = "http://general.gamerfeed.com/gf/news/7478/">GamerFeed</a> has published an article with Todd Hollenshead about the upcomming DOOM 3: The Movie. Todd said that the script is almost finished and he'll be ecstatic if the movie is out by the end of next year. Read full aticle <a href = "http://general.gamerfeed.com/gf/news/7478/">here</a>.
